{"ID":"20260305082130-i59w051","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-i59w051","title":"模板","type":"doc","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082201-bu319ct","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","Properties":{"id":"20260305082201-bu319ct"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"eWFtbA=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"---\ntitle: 模板\ndate created: 星期二, 十月 21日 2025, 1:38:03 下午\ndate modified: 星期二, 十一月 4日 2025, 2:37:20 下午\n---"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-btpgoe5","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-btpgoe5","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1 模版的概念"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-hbqkyld","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-hbqkyld","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-vsp1bur","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-vsp1bur","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-g3h67xx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-g3h67xx","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"模板是 C++ 中实现\u003cfont color=\"#4f81bd\"\u003e泛型编程\u003c/font\u003e的核心机制，它允许编写与具体数据类型无关的通用代码。模板本质上是一种\u003cfont color=\"#4f81bd\"\u003e代码生成工具\u003c/font\u003e，编译器在编译时根据实际使用的数据类型自动生成相应的具体代码；"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-cj9ftvb","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-cj9ftvb","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-kx0hwcc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-kx0hwcc","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"模板是对一族函数或类的描述，是参数化的函数和类；"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-zqzfttf","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-zqzfttf","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-u1jeqbj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-u1jeqbj","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"模板是一种参数化的多态性工具，为各种逻辑功能相同而数据类型不同的程序提供一种代码共享的机制。模板不是以数据为参数，而是以它所使用的数据类型为参数；"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-gc9sylv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-gc9sylv","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"核心思想"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-snv8uqi","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-snv8uqi","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-mo4utfz","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"1.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-mo4utfz","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-5xh692s","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-5xh692s","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"类型参数化："},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"将数据类型作为参数传递给模板；"},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"相同的算法逻辑可以应用于不同的数据类型；"},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"实现 “一次编写，多处使用” 的目标。"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-wyw67s8","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"2.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":2,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"Mi4=","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-wyw67s8","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-f6i9qk4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-f6i9qk4","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"编译时多态："},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"模板在编译时实例化，而不是运行时；"},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"编译器为每种使用的数据类型生成特定的代码版本；"},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"没有运行时性能开销。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-0prs27u","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-0prs27u","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2 模版的基本分类"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-2rimcis","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-2rimcis","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-ocik9h6","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"1.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-ocik9h6","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-oc1q3rb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-oc1q3rb","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"block-ref","TextMarkBlockRefID":"20260305082130-3m0qivo","TextMarkBlockRefSubtype":"d","TextMarkTextContent":"函数模板"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-em6tz6g","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"2.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":2,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"Mi4=","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-em6tz6g","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-8noevt6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-8noevt6","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"block-ref","TextMarkBlockRefID":"20260305082130-c4p6j76","TextMarkBlockRefSubtype":"d","TextMarkTextContent":"类模板"}]}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-153680t","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"3.","List